-removing air purifiers available. Many air filters claim to reduce odors, but few are specifically targeted at the problem. The Sunpentown Heavy Duty AC-2102 features a five-filter system with UV light, all designed to capture and eliminate noxious odors. However, for as good as it is at removing stench, it lacks the proper equipment to capture pollen, dust and other indoor pollutants. In addition to lacking total air-cleaning potential, the Heavy Duty is large and loud, limiting its use to large rooms.","The primary problem with the SPT Heavy Duty AC-2102 is that few people have large rooms filled with odors in their homes. Specialization is not a problem, but we would like to see an improved HEPA air filter to capture the smallest particulates. Also, at its highest setting, the air purifier is obnoxiously loud. What it lacks in allergen and pollutant filtration, the Heavy Duty makes up for with its bacteria-killing UV light.","It is important to note that the ACT-2102 is not certified by the California Air Resource Board for low to no ozone emissions. Many studies show that UV lights can generate ozone, a particle found naturally in the upper atmosphere. Human lungs should not be exposed to too much ozone, so if you have breathing-related issues, this air purifier may exacerbate them.","The SPT air purifier also has a filter monitor and an air-quality sensor. The filter monitor tells you when you need to replace the air filter. The air-quality sensor estimates the amount of indoor pollution and controls the air purifier&#39;s fan speed. When you turn on the auto mode, the Heavy Duty filters the air and maintains a clean environment. You can also set an operation time between one and eight hours. After the timed operation, the Heavy Duty enters a sleep mode to save energy. Finally, this unit comes with a remote control.","Sunpentown&#39;s customer service could use some improvement. If you need help, you have to contact customer service representatives by phone or email; there is no live chat option. The website lacks a FAQs section and downloadable user manuals. The SPT Heavy Duty AC-2102 comes with a one-year warranty."]},"id":"614adbbf-9b7f-48d2-a807-0bd9da29512b","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"93b91ccb-a426-4c15-925a-5d7a87e19766","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The SPT Heavy Duty AC-2102 is an odor-removing air purifier with an optional UV light for VOC filtration. However, it is extremely large and loud, and it does a poor job at removing allergens. It has a long list of extra features, including an air-quality sensor and remote control. If you need an air filter to take control of noxious odors but not allergens, the SPT Heavy Duty AC-2102 is a great option."]},"id":"1ee61941-78c5-4e3e-9784-3a5c170ff822","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_56447","url":"/spt-heavy-duty-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-05-20T20:16:45Z","datePublished":"2013-05-20T20:16:45Z","name":"SPT Heavy Duty AC-2102","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Air Purifiers here. There are not many odor-removing air purifiers available.","review":{"verdict":"The SPT Heavy Duty AC-2102 is an odor-removing air purifier for large rooms, but its HEPA air filter is not CARB certified for low to no ozone emission.","pros":["The SPT Heavy Duty AC-2102 utilizes a five-filter system to capture large indoor pollutants and reduce indoor odors."],"cons":["This air purifier is not Energy Star verified or CARB certified."]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: This review has been re